"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我真係冇人約，生日都係冇人理<br />\n明明我次次都有幫佢地搞飯局，搞生日會<br />\n但係當我生日個陣時個個都潛曬水，節日更加係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd843f2bda07c5448a7347e3b68a72311c8aa6f","tid":955540,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:21:39.000Z","msg":"一撚樣咁濟<br />\n唯一唔同係我有其他無拖拍嘅朋友過下節<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3fd8dc7e131874f35bd789d3d80dfc8ce46c8f","tid":955540,"uid":63762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"有樣有錢<br />\n自然有人搵你玩"},{"pid":"f7ad2ddc75b62eba301a7f87548b9b4290f7c611","tid":955540,"uid":3339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"殺手咪永遠都係一個人囉"},{"pid":"b8e55656455e41983e53e1f52223d6d896103258","tid":955540,"uid":211744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a0bd1991b8756666445685bf7cd92bc08d281af","tid":955540,"uid":55923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T18:55:37.000Z","msg":"識一個人有啲似你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話聖誕無人約  轉頭將自己個schedule排到full哂  約佢要提早一個月  仲要隨時畀佢放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"一定唔會係我 我冇放過人飛機<br />\n我會提早約定朋友<br />\n好多時我都係比人放飛機果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b85b3e5804e7cec44ce70588075fe66121d7c81","tid":955540,"uid":211744,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0cd843f2bda07c5448a7347e3b68a72311c8aa6f","tid":955540,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T21:21:39.000Z","msg":"一撚樣咁濟<br />\n唯一唔同係我有其他無拖拍嘅朋友過下節<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"我最後一個老死都出左pool<br />\n好似比人搶左個女咁 好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e9a859619ae187ea77db5039a95f0d27bd999b","tid":955540,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"你叫個連朋友都冇既人情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n融入唔到任何圈子"},{"pid":"26c96ac76453511298c93f64ed8e367f92dfd104","tid":955540,"uid":71756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"以為自己開po"},{"pid":"e2b66ba540018fa4cd6753dd3be4810ed24ede41","tid":955540,"uid":49015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63af486851fbbf6c7f7ac5f41a2619371ebc1ef1","tid":955540,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T18:56:03.000Z","msg":"絲打 同你一模一樣<br />\n利申: 藍絲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多 但我朋友都唔多"},{"pid":"6b36df4bdfbbf71e5a67d8a8d4c80ae14096e5ca","tid":955540,"uid":44142,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"因為你對人太好，人地未必會珍惜。<br />\n人係獨立個體，朋友既野都係過客，講緣份。有長有短。<br />\n20頭果陣同樓主相反，朋友唔少，有交心，有酒肉。<br />\n人大左，放工就想摺埋，再唔係同另一半煮下野食，行下街，放下狗。<br />\n真係交心既一年見1-2次巳經好好"},{"pid":"e6f40c3e54318fe349566214c7befc885f8ad51e","tid":955540,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"重點 無樣無身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4847e1261d02318a5dd959f13f56b3f3dfdf82b","tid":955540,"uid":121349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"樓主已經畢咗業全職做野？ 20出頭咁快有能力自已一個搬出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0b4b809ba28685692dcfd96323cee0f595b11a","tid":955540,"uid":225219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T12:38:51.000Z","msg":"好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左唔係自己住同埋仲有幾個單身fd一齊過節<br />\n今年生日屋企人冇主動幫自己慶祝連蛋糕都係我話好想食要求佢地買比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一年屋企人仲試過攞親戚買黎我屋企既蛋糕當生日蛋糕同我切<br />\n每次識親新朋友十個有十一個都覺得我拍緊拖或者拍過幾次拖<br />\n話A0佢地就會話係咪我眼角高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909242912eab6ca923d743f1104c09d8a62b46bb","tid":955540,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"每次識新朋友都會被認為係現充 一定有男朋友<br />\n話冇 其實係A0就比人話：你實係怕羞唔想講 收收埋埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地客氣說話咋，唔通直接講話: A0?我睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢d心照啦洗乜講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}